{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":795282,"duration_api_ms":720347,"num_turns":59,"result":"## Summary\n\n**Bug:** BUG-PM-013 — `track_order` button shows \"Стейк\" dish popup instead of `OrderStatusScreen`\n\n**Root Cause:** The `CONFIRMATION_AUTO_DISMISS_MS = 10000` (10-second timer) in `showConfirmation()` created a race condition:\n1. Timer fires after 10s → `setView(\"menu\")`, `setConfirmationData(null)` → confirmation overlay unmounts\n2. Menu grid renders at the same screen position where the confirmation overlay was\n3. User's pending touch/click event falls through to a dish card (\"Стейк\") in the menu grid\n4. `DishReviewsModal` opens with \"Стейк\" details → user sees a product popup instead of the order status screen\n\n**Fix (260303-04):**\n- Removed `CONFIRMATION_AUTO_DISMISS_MS` constant entirely\n- Removed `confirmationTimerRef` and all timer setup/cleanup code\n- `showConfirmation()` no longer starts an auto-dismiss timer — users navigate via 3 explicit buttons: \"Back to Menu\", \"My Orders\", \"Track Order\"\n- `handleTrackOrder()` simplified (no timer cleanup needed)\n- `dismissConfirmation()` simplified (no timer cleanup needed)\n\n**Changes:**\n- 5 code removals/simplifications across `showConfirmation`, `dismissConfirmation`, `handleTrackOrder`, and cleanup `useEffect`\n- BUGS.md updated with BUG-PM-013\n\n**RELEASE:** `pages/PublicMenu/260303-04 x RELEASE.jsx`\n**Git:** `081af18`","stop_reason":null,"session_id":"60873042-7b75-4f37-a34c-807acde7578a","total_cost_usd":3.30631225,"usage":{"input_tokens":47,"cache_creation_input_tokens":106071,"cache_read_input_tokens":3583293,"output_tokens":33829,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":106071,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":47,"outputTokens":33829,"cacheReadInput